    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "The sysinfo stats for the current release show only 45 users (1%) on Windows using a 2.0 scale who would benefit from the HiDPI features.  This compares badly with the 12% of windows players who are running a non-integer scale between 1 and 2 and will most likely see graphical regressions.\r\n\r\n46% of our OSX players are running with the 2.0 scale."
